name: Irene
about: I am an Adult and Geriatric Nurse Practitioner who is mainly reading NP board certification review books these days. I love books about people, people and their interactions and with each other and the human spirit. I'm a fan of authors: Grisham, Rowling, Tan, Ha Jin, Anchee Min, Barack Obama. Even if they have crappy books (Grisham currently), I'll still stick with them. I admit, I am extremely biased towards fiction about Chinese people. I love reading the history (emperors, empresses, Cultural Revolution, prejudice) in the fiction. I would be happiest if EVERY bookstore had a Chinese book section for me.
